This paper is about text summarization, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR). The use of reinforcement learning (RL) and neural networks (NN) also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
